summary: Vendored the runnable app, moved the marketing site into landing/, and modernized the toolchain.
---

Dictaro entered the umbrella: the **runnable app** was vendored in and the
marketing site moved into `landing/`. The toolchain moved to TypeScript 7
beta, and the source tree was renamed from *aylith-apps* to *aylith-labs*.
